Interface PopCanRackListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AbstractHardwareListener

    public interface PopCanRackListener
extends AbstractHardwareListener
    Listens for events emanating from a pop can rack.

        void popCansLoaded(PopCanRack rack,
